5:
"DAN making a steady recovery as
Noxel Group nearly finishes
rebuilding its foundation..."
10:
Not much left for me to do except
clear the way for her. That's what a
bullet's good for, right?
14: Hello, Bulleta. Still alive, I hope?
18:
Gotta admit, the last time I worked
24-7 was back when I first joined.
22:
But don't you worry. Your Bullet can
handle this much, easy!
26:
...Again with that? I thought you were
the Bullet of Freedom, not Love's
Bullet.
28:
That aside, I came with a job. I
prepared you new equipment to go
along with it, too.
32: ...Planning to send me off to battle?
35:
Fine by me. I'll clear the path for you,
partner.
37: Wherever you need me, I'll be there!
44: Uh... This isn't what I meant.
51:
What's she so upset about? We're at
the beach! In swimsuits! Sun's out,
guns out!
55:
It seems Love forced her to take a
vacation since she was overworking
herself. Personally, I understand
where Bulleta is coming from...
59:
It's not like I was working THAT hard!
Anyone can manage two or three
days without sleep, right?
64:
Exactly. I can go at least five days
without rest—
68:
Eugh, no one likes listening to people
brag about self-torture, dude!
73:
I'm not bragging! Honestly? I don't
think I'm doing enough!
75:
Love's working her ass off lately.
Even a regular nobody pretending
to be a somebody would have a
hard time keeping up.
78:
...I figured the least I could do was...
clear the way for her as much as
possible—
81:
You, uh... You're sure doing a lot
without her asking.
86: Is... Is that a bad thing?!
91:
Sho, you can't just blurt stuff out like
that!
96:
Well, well, well. Pythica, looks like
we've got someone else who could
use a lesson in relaxation.
100:
Right? This isn't happy and healthy
behavior!
110:
Sounds like it's time to bring out the
ultra-deluxe-luxury spa ticket for
our unhealthy friend here!
114:
We'll make you relax so hard that
you end up crying from all the
pent-up stress and never want to
work again!
118:
...You sure that's supposed to make
me happy and healthy?
122:
You're here to refresh yourself, right?
Whether you like it or not! So you
better give it everything you've got!
126:
Love even found the time to get that 
amazing swimsuit for you, even though 
she's a super-busy, big-shot CEO! 
No sense in letting it go to waste!
134:
Wow, did you see that? She
changed the INSTANT I said Love's
name!
138: D-do you think they really are...
142:
Are what? You're not thinking of
something totally off base, are you?
147:
Not that I'm one to talk, but...
Sometimes, it's pretty nice to just
take it easy for a bit.
155:
The Bullet of Freedom is gonna
spend her summer having a blast
with all of you!
159:
Bring the fun on! If we're doing this,
then we're doing it right!
168:
I wanna check out the pool area
after the spa! They've apparently
got some extreme obstacle courses
set up this year!
174:
Yeah? Fine by me! I can handle
anything!
179:
Sounds like you're having fun
already, Bulleta.
184: L-Love? H-how... Why are you here?
187:
I never said the job required us to
both be in Qualia City... or that you'd
be doing it alone.
191:
You could've told me you'd be
tagging along!
194:
I wasn't planning to in the beginning.
I only meant to observe and make
sure you were actually taking a
break.
198:
Huh? Are you... upset about
something?
203:
Oh, I know! We got too close to your
Bulleta, didn't we—
207:
N-no, that's not... I... I came because I
had a message to convey!
210: Oho? So you guys really are...
219:
Bulleta! Your outfit is a little TOO well
done, so make sure you don't draw
attention to yourself! Do I make
myself clear?
226:
You telling me not to be loud?
Because I came here to cut loose,
didn't I?
231:
Yes, you did! Just... focus on that
part!
